Description :
Management of a customer issue through a guided process and interactions with the relevant stakeholders. The case could be created and managed proactively (automated) or in response to a customer request.

Description :
Management (creation, classification, validation and publication workflows) and contextualized distribution (classification, search and artificial intelligence based on case history) of operational knowledge artifacts, organised in articles, aiming at helping the agent to answer the customer through the reading of the knowledge or the direct sharing of it to the customer.

Description :
Management of internal and private set of conversations aiming at enabling stakeholders of our ecosystem (vendors, providers...) to collaborate in order to efficiently resolve a customer case.

Description :
Set of capabilities to integrate and contextualize the usage of business tools to facilitate and optimize the gesture of the agent in processing the customer requests.

Description :
Management of customer appointments for any business interaction, both physical/onsite and remote appointments.

Description :
Capability to manage competences and availability of a team dedicated to the customer service and interactions handling

Description :
Capability to supervise key operational indicators of a contact center to manage daily activities.

Description :
Capability to analyse overall contact center data to work on strategical decisions as well as operational organisation shifts.

Description :
Capability to plan and distribute outbound customer interactions to a contact center or customer service team.

Description :
Capability to supervise and control SLAs on top of key indicators of a customer service to control service quality.

Description :

Description :
Capability to interact with a customer through an automated text or voice conversation based on a natural language based conversation tree.

Description :
Capability to automatically interact with a customer through a phone call

Description :
Management of customer conversations between the customer service and the customer through public messaging channels (SMS, WhatsApp, Messenger…).

Description :
Management of customer conversations between the customer service and the customer through chatlive solution (i.e. synchronous textual conversation through web and mobile).

Description :
Management of an entry customer request provided through a mail form.

Description :
